rows.label: qst200602_msg0001
rows.name:
What ails you, my Driver? You
look befuddled as a loon.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0003
rows.name:
No... I'm just happy that you seem
to have got your motivation back.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0004
rows.name:
It's nothing. I'm just pleased that
you're looking motivated now!

rows.label: qst200602_msg0005
rows.name:
No...there is no trouble. I am just
happy that you seem motivated now.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0006
rows.name:
No problems here. I'm just
happy that you're looking
good and motivated!

rows.label: qst200602_msg0007
rows.name:
Well, if my attitude pleases
you, I trust you will work
hard to serve my aims.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0008
rows.name:
To protect a true and loyal
retainer, I would gladly draw
out the depths of my strength.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0009
rows.name:
The depths of your strength,
huh... Sounds pretty unbeatable.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0010
rows.name:
The depths of your strength, eh?
Guess we'll be pretty unbeatable.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0011
rows.name:
The depths of your strength?
I could not ask for a more
dependable ally.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0012
rows.name:
The depths of your strength?
Damn, those are pretty deep.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0013
rows.name:
Hahaha! Your king will
not be easily defeated!

rows.label: qst200602_msg0014
rows.name:
For the sake of restoring my
kingdom, I will spare no effort!
